caption: Came here for Restaurant Week, and I was pleasantly surprised. I has the pork belly taco, the pastrami taco, and paid extra for the Tuna taco. Omg!
Great taco, also had the option to sub in tofu

Trataron de hacer tacos fancys, pero no tienen sabor, las tortillas se rompen, pedimos salsa y nos trajeron dip sin sabor, otra salsa que se ve que quisieron hacer Nancy y sabe a Valentina dulce el servicio umm  malo

Such an awesome place! The server who helped us from start to finish was so nice and helpful! As someone who is vegetarian it is tough to find variety when I eat at restaurants. This place had a few delicious options! The carrot “chorizo” taco was hands down my favorite!

Wild Taco is such a smooth vibe to be new and the owners are very pleasant and accommodating. Ryan who is a part owner, went above and beyond to provide us service during the NCAA Tournament. I highly suggest this restaurant, because of the great food/portion size.  The establishment is super clean and cozy.  The outdoor patio is nice as well. Grab a margarita and vibe out.  Ryan shoutout to you and team.

We were not expecting much when we tried it but we were really surprised by the great quality of the food and the fantastic service! A great addition to the neighbourhood! We will definitely be coming back!

Had a great lunch today at Wild Taco with family. I had the protien bowl - it was truly delicious! and my daughters had a variety of tacos, also excellent! We topped the meal off with desert nachos and churros. The staff coudn't have been nicer. This restaurant is a wonderful addition to Old Town - will be back!
Great, friendly service, tasty tacos, guacamole sides and even dessert! This place is a worth a try and will be great for tacos and margs outdoors come summer!
Dined in for lunch and I really enjoyed both the food and service! Great addition to the neighborhood
Food was great! Highly recommend Wild Taco

What a great new addition to Wells Street. We happen to stumble across this gem on a Sunday afternoon. The place is really cute with outdoor dining. We ordered a couple tacos and a bowl that were delicious.  We will definitely come back. I can’t wait to sit outside

So excited this is in our neighborhood! Great options for everyone, including vegan/vegetarian. Highly recommend the Ruben and the tuna!! Such a great atmosphere, and clean environment! Love that nicer weather allows for the garage door to be open so the entire restaurant has a nice airflow! The staff & ownership are super friendly, and definitely make you feel right at home here in old town ❤️ kid/family friendly, and pups allowed to join sidewalk seating!
Not impressed at all with the food. This place won't last past the summer. Seems like they are not even prepared to be open yet.

I came by the soft opening day, coming from the restaurant industry I know that that day is like a trial run but Wild Taco was on top of everything! The staff was so incredibly warm and quick, food was fantastic and there were so many options for someone like me who has a ton of dietary restrictions! And I’d be silly not to mention the amazing owners who were there greeting everyone who walked through the door! Go try it, you won’t regret it

Ryan, Trevor, Niko, Matt, Jazmyne are amazing people as for 1 unknown individual who I don't wanna speak off well he isn't so good but anywho Ryan is gonna be the best to run the place cause he is the only one who knows how to do so might stop by 1 day that's if I am in the area or if that IT Individual isn't there but yeah 😉

Absolutely love Wild Taco. The place is soo cute and such a fun place to take friends out for some delicious tacos!! Highly recommend the guacamole with their homemade tortilla chips! The owners and staff are so friendly and made the experience whole!

It's opening day!!! We stopped in and tried 6 different tacos and the dessert nachos! All of it was really great and the ingredients were super fresh. My personal favorites were the Birria (beef & bone marrow) and the Crispy Fish. Will 100% be back.
Great tacos, great food! The manager and all the staff are so nice. Highly recommend.
Delicious new spot on wells! The tuna and chicken taco were great.
